redirects.description: Google Meet link - redirection to next account
redirects.patternDesc: You might have 2 accounts logged in on your PC - one is your school account, and one is your personal account. This redirect redirects all Google Meet meeting links to school accounts. Does not apply to normal meet.google.com links.

redirects.description: Redirect Google Classroom to second account logged in to your PC
redirects.patternDesc: You might have 2 accounts logged in on your PC - one is your school account, and one is your personal account. This redirect redirects Google Classroom homepage (classroom.google.com) to school accounts. Does not apply to normal other links for tasks.
